Details can be observed in above web address and Tasaki falls under Fund III of Portfolio companies. There is no natural person single beneficial owner to be filled up to your field list since PE Funds have multiple fund contributors and the fund managers manage the portfolios companies and decide either to go on an Initial Public Offering (IPO), sell to same industry company or sell to same Private Equity Funds depending on the circumstances, depending on the market and performances of the company.  Usually Private Equity Funds operates by investments from pension funds, endowment funds and high net worth individuals and there is no natural person single beneficial owner as well as the fund is neither a Public Listed Company nor Publicly Non-listed Company. The fields provided in this form are not adequate to fill up necessary information. The attached person is the representative person of Myanmar Tasaki Co., Ltd. and he does not own Myanmar Tasaki Co., Ltd. Due to the lack of fields, we can fill up to this level to disclose beneficial ownership requirements of MEITI.
